                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Hutchinson</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-05-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 24, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hutchinson reports that court of first instance gave decision against the
                    New York and Bermudez Company last Saturday on Hamilton concession, annulling
                    concession, and damages to be assessed by experts.</p>
                <p>The case will be appealed to full court.)</p>
            </div>
